Extracted Variables:
- \( x \): number of low-powered air conditioners
- \( y \): number of high-powered air conditioners

Extracted Constraints:
- Cooling Capacity: \( 12x + 17y \geq 250 \)
- Electricity Usage: \( 150x + 250y \leq 3400 \)
- Limit on Low-powered Models: \( x \leq 0.3(x+y) \)
- Minimum High-powered Models: \( y \geq 7 \)
- Non-negativity: \( x, y \geq 0 \)

Extracted Objective:
- Minimize \( Z = x + y \)
